    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-strung powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver 333 horsepower to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term durability, this chassis has received critical subframe reinforcement and upgraded trailing arm bushings. The suspension geometry remains tight, providing the communicative feedback and precise turn-in characteristic of the E46 platform. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the vehicle is in excellent mechanical health, offering a visceral driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
