    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s been treated with a lot of love? I\u2019m parting ways with my car, and it\u2019s honestly in such great shape. It drives incredibly smooth and has been really well-maintained over the years. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of use here and there, but nothing that takes away from how solid and comfortable it feels on the road. It's been a fantastic car for me, and I'm sure it'll be just as great for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
